{"tid":1790580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台鐵「光復>高雄」車票成為最新紀念品，一夕間破紀錄光速售罄","createTime":"2019-12-20T06:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T15:42:50.000Z","uid":52658,"like":81,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"9317ec1031b3b221a0a4f129750226ba981f2adb","tid":1790580,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T06:08:44.000Z","msg":"罷韓、挺韓遊行21日將同時於高雄登場，早在遊行開始前，罷韓團體「公民割草行動」發放的罷韓貼紙就常常供不應求。有民眾因為搶不到罷韓貼紙，竟突發奇想買了從花蓮光復開往高雄的台鐵車票，網友也大讚這張票簡直超越「追分成功」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6Yxhch.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6Yxhch.jpg&h=b8c06002&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2njP3Sv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2njP3Sv.jpg&h=f3ec67fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n罷韓團體設計的「光復高雄」等罷韓貼紙常供不應求。（擷取自「公民割草行動」臉書粉絲專頁）"},{"pid":"44216404ed7b61b42c03f0c9a3a6307caa6114cb","tid":1790580,"uid":52658,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T06:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CDgCtjF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCDgCtjF.jpg&h=df2f8214&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45f1e2c2ed3b8a8859252b713fbb2784bf9a58bd","tid":1790580,"uid":105114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T06:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f119b70e1129e8c1950bbfd893ca763fc813534c","tid":1790580,"uid":52658,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T06:16:03.000Z","msg":"時代力量可以印呢個貼紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣鄉民可以去黃國昌ig提議下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復高雄<br />\n時代力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmo